    "learnmode": {
      "instruction": {
        "en": "Universal Zigbee Device (DIY + Standard ZCL)\n\n1. Put your device in pairing mode\n2. For Sonoff: Hold button 5+ seconds\n3. For ESP32/PTVO: Press boot button\n4. For Danfoss/Legrand/Schneider: Follow manufacturer pairing\n\nCapabilities auto-discovered from ZCL clusters.\n\nSupported: Sonoff, eWeLink, Danfoss, Legrand, Schneider, Bosch, Niko, ESP32, PTVO, CC2652, routers.",
        "fr": "Appareil Zigbee DIY générique (ESP32, PTVO, CC253x, etc.)\n\n1. Mettez votre appareil DIY en mode appairage\n2. Pour ESP32: Appuyez sur boot ou déclenchez l'appairage\n3. Pour PTVO: Maintenez le bouton 5+ secondes\n4. Pour CC253x: Redémarrez ou réinitialisez\n\nLes capacités seront auto-découvertes depuis les clusters ZCL.\n\nSupporté: ESP32-C6, ESP32-H2, PTVO, CC2530/31, CC2652, routeurs Zigbee."
      }
    }
  },
  "settings": [
    {
      "type": "group",
      "label": {
        "en": "🔧 Device Information",
        "fr": "🔧 Informations Appareil"
      },
      "children": [
        {
          "id": "diy_manufacturer_name",
          "type": "label",
          "label": {
            "en": "Manufacturer",
            "fr": "Fabricant"
          },
          "value": "DIY"
        },
        {
          "id": "diy_model_id",
          "type": "label",
          "label": {
            "en": "Model ID",
